        "title": "工信部：加强高端光电芯片和器件研发，到2028年城域算力1毫秒时延圈覆盖率不低于75%",
        "uri": "https://wallstreetcn.com/articles/3774307"
      },
      "author": {
        "avatar": "https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/714916ad-9609-4245-94b4-dfe9518a63c3",
        "display_name": "万小婷",
        "id": 120000003969,
